title: Svartkonst- Black Metal
description:
SVARTKONST was formed in 2012, Sweden. Since it is impossible to find fellow musicians with the same musical taste in my area I started to record my own songs. My music is rooted in Black and Thrash Metal, but I often include many other influences as well, such as Punk.
